name: Harmonic Buddy 2
description:
The Harmonic Buddy is one of the guardians of the Harmonic Garden. It flies high to show the best way. Brings good energies, spread life, love, respect to the nature and grow the hope of a better planet to all live beens. Let your imagination go beyond to see the flowers full your heart.

This piece is part of the second edition of Pupila Dilatada's psychedelic exhibition!
